          "reviewTitle": "My FAVORITE Concealer!!",
          "reviewText": "I will forever be a L.A. Girl Pro Concealer girly. Out of all the concealers I\u2019ve used (even expensive brands) this product never disappoints. I like that you can build on it. It doesn\u2019t cake up after hours of wear. You can blend it right away to get a great coverage. One of my favorite products!!",
          "reviewDate": "Reviewed in the United States on March 28, 2026",
